    @GeneratedValue(strategy=GenerationType.SEQUENCE, generator=&quot;step_id_seq&quot;)
    @SequenceGenerator(name=&quot;step_id_seq&quot;, sequenceName=&quot;step_id_seq&quot;)

Now, you can call sequence using NativeQuery:

